This middleware provides "traditional" php variables parsed from request:
php_compat += array(
  '_GET' => array(),
  '_COOKIE' => ArrayAccess + ->setcookie(), ->setrawcookie(),
  '_POST' => array(),
  '_FILES' => array(),

  + emulate stdin using smth like http://code.google.com/p/phpstringstream/source/browse/trunk/stringstream.php
)

